Package: DS1G12
Type: Package
Title: Analyzing DRG Data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Hexiuli Huang
Maintainer: Hexiuli Huang <hexiuli.huang@email.com>
Description: This package provides tools for analyzing hospital-specific charges data 
    from Medicare Inpatient Prospective Payment System (IPPS) for Fiscal Year (FY) 2011. 
    It includes functions to create boxplots of payments by DRG code and calculate 
    statistics for average Medicare payments across all DRG codes. The package is designed 
    for educational purposes and serves as an example for building R packages.
